{"tid":1214202,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［自己救］［十小辣］食肆衞生小隊","createTime":"2019-06-13T03:44:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T04:08:01.000Z","uid":16859,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"aec2dc2e33225106c187c903562a273bbad2516d","tid":1214202,"uid":16859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T03:44:46.000Z","msg":"我諗大家好多時出街都會見到啲唔太乾淨既餐廳，作為良好市民，我地又點可以唔出聲篤導一下食肆衛生呢？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.1823.gov.hk/big5/FAQ/009009/index.shtm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.1823.gov.hk%2Fbig5%2FFAQ%2F009009%2Findex.shtm&d=lXSk0n6jiDV9AqJ6X6RhLgmr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=a72ef22b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.1823.gov.hk/big5/FAQ/009009/index.shtm</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">如市民在食肆用膳時發現食物不潔、有異物、或不宜食用，可向食環署作出投訴。</span><br />\n<br />\n衛生黑點（有待更新整合）：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gW0TBoM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgW0TBoM.png&h=c2897e70&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MQmb7vT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMQmb7vT.jpg&h=115e41bb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4ec89a787e93dd5d9787df3e87d016e4eda7feaa","tid":1214202,"uid":16859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T03:57:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"01126f372a99c83dcfca7b538f866188c5ad0353","tid":1214202,"uid":159414,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T04:02:06.000Z","msg":"加一<br />\n<br />\n旺角雅蘭對面間活壽司<br />\n<br />\n個壽司師傅同個西裝阿叔<br />\n啲學生有學唔返，周圍搞事<br />\n咪撚阻住我搵錢啊<br />\n肯定有推手，搵人出嚟搞事啦"},{"pid":"5fa1840370de629912f848e129e3c6dc4968e08d","tid":1214202,"uid":170249,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T04:03:45.000Z","msg":"真心覺得呢班廢中 冇得救<br />\n<br />\n明明為香港為下一代戰鬥<br />\n<br />\n仲要俾佢地講到有錢收咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n傻唔緊要 但唔係咁腦殘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\